FBIS4-11385 "drlat080_m_94010" FBIS-LAT-94-080 Daily Report 25 Apr 1994 Brazil Government Guarantees Embraer's $172-Million Debt Government Guarantees Embraer's $172-Million Debt PY2604002394 Brasilia Voz do Brasil Network in Portuguese 2200 GMT 25 Apr 94 PY2604002394 Brasilia Voz do Brasil Network Portuguese BFN [Text] President Itamar Franco has signed a provisional measure that empowers the federal government to guarantee a Bank of Brazil $172-million loan to the Brazilian Aeronautics Company [Embraer]. The loan will be used to increase Embraer's capital through the issuance of new regular shares that will be endorsed by the federal government.
